Package GIS

Class MetaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • GIS.MetaData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Meta_data

    public class MetaData
extends java.lang.Object
implements Meta_data
    Meta data object represents all the information about the object itself, mostly about the GISElement object. Contains data as mac address, ssid address and more.

      • MetaData

        public MetaData​(java.lang.String mac,
                java.lang.String ssid,
                java.lang.String authmode,
                java.lang.String firstseen,
                java.lang.String channel,
                java.lang.String rssi,
                java.lang.String accuracyMeters,
                java.lang.String type)
        Creates a new MetaData object for GISElement.
        Parameters:
        mac - String of machine id.
        ssid - String display name of device.
        authmode - String type of encryption.
        firstseen - String exact date of device been seen.
        channel - String channel which used for transmission.
        rssi - String Received Signal Strength Indicator show from 0 to 255 the strength of signal the closer to 0 the better.
        accuracyMeters - String the accuracy of device location.
        type - String type of transmission to device.
